WEBVTT

01:25.810 --> 01:34.850
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.440 --> 01:37.840
[Episode 13]

01:45.039 --> 01:45.440
Hello.

01:45.680 --> 01:46.539
Zhuang Zhuang?

01:47.140 --> 01:47.830
Yes, I am.

01:48.259 --> 01:49.450
I'm head of Design Team No. 2.

01:49.450 --> 01:50.070
My name is Toby.

01:50.070 --> 01:50.570
Nice to meet you.

01:50.570 --> 01:51.430
Care for a tour?

01:51.509 --> 01:52.009
Sure.

01:52.200 --> 01:52.729
Let's go.

01:54.200 --> 01:55.280
This is the conference area.

01:55.280 --> 01:56.560
But we don't use it very often.

01:56.560 --> 01:57.729
It's poorly designed,

01:57.729 --> 01:59.190
so Ms. Yue doesn't like it.

01:59.509 --> 02:01.370
Upstairs is the styling section.

02:01.430 --> 02:01.890
Here...

02:02.370 --> 02:03.770
is our main battlefield.

02:06.450 --> 02:07.430
This is the tailoring area,

02:07.430 --> 02:08.080
where ready-to-wear

02:08.080 --> 02:08.970
clothes are altered.

02:08.970 --> 02:09.460
Our own factory

02:09.460 --> 02:10.780
covers the massive production.

02:10.780 --> 02:12.680
This area is for selecting fabrics.

02:12.680 --> 02:14.880
This space is taken by Design Team No. 2.

02:15.060 --> 02:16.000
And that area is used

02:16.000 --> 02:17.040
for accessory design.

02:17.040 --> 02:18.010
This is my desk.

02:18.520 --> 02:19.650
Yours is over there.

02:19.750 --> 02:20.400
Got it.

02:20.900 --> 02:21.740
As for this place,

02:21.740 --> 02:22.630
it is where we make reports

02:22.630 --> 02:23.500
to Ms. Yue.

02:24.400 --> 02:25.770
Where is Ms. Yue?

02:25.840 --> 02:27.170
I should go say hi to her.

02:28.120 --> 02:29.920
The "tiger's den" is over there.

02:31.280 --> 02:32.130
"Tiger"?

02:32.610 --> 02:34.340
The kind that eats human flesh.

02:34.530 --> 02:35.860
If she doesn't call for you,

02:35.860 --> 02:37.990
I suggest you do not easily go meet her.

02:38.530 --> 02:39.630
Aren't I here to work

02:39.630 --> 02:40.630
as her assistant?

02:40.800 --> 02:42.280
That's merely a title.

02:42.360 --> 02:43.960
What matters is what you want to do here.

02:43.960 --> 02:45.250
If you want to learn fashion design,

02:45.250 --> 02:46.380
then spend more time

02:46.400 --> 02:47.660
with Design Team No. 2.

02:47.750 --> 02:49.280
If you want to learn styling,

02:49.280 --> 02:50.280
then go upstairs.

02:50.430 --> 02:51.430
What's your idea?

02:51.470 --> 02:51.900
I...

02:52.530 --> 02:53.690
I definitely want to learn

02:53.690 --> 02:54.930
as much as I can from you.

02:54.930 --> 02:56.500
I'll go on a bit more then.

02:57.120 --> 02:58.079
Do you usually read?

02:58.079 --> 02:58.870
What kind of books?

02:58.870 --> 03:00.030
Any kind.

03:00.240 --> 03:00.900
You can find

03:01.070 --> 03:01.930
the latest issues

03:01.930 --> 03:03.560
of all sorts of fashion magazines here.

03:03.560 --> 03:05.080
But whether you understand
the content or not

03:05.080 --> 03:05.870
is on you.

03:06.500 --> 03:07.310
I have things to do.

03:07.310 --> 03:08.520
Will you be okay on your own?

03:08.520 --> 03:09.010
Yes.

03:09.090 --> 03:10.180
You are still on probation.

03:10.180 --> 03:10.870
Do your best.

03:10.870 --> 03:11.410
Thanks.

03:19.290 --> 03:23.230
[Police Office]

03:25.840 --> 03:26.370
Sit down.

03:28.640 --> 03:29.290
I dare not.

03:29.810 --> 03:30.410
Sit down.

03:31.280 --> 03:32.780
What, are you scared?

03:33.620 --> 03:35.079
I'm worried about being wronged!

03:35.079 --> 03:35.690
"Scared"?

03:36.560 --> 03:38.160
You were caught red-handed.

03:38.620 --> 03:39.820
You can't be wronged.

03:40.090 --> 03:41.930
I was tricked by Li Xiaobo!

03:42.210 --> 03:43.000
He told me

03:43.000 --> 03:44.710
he needed to buy tickets for his company,

03:44.710 --> 03:46.630
but he couldn't stand
waiting in the queue anymore.

03:46.630 --> 03:47.410
I figured

03:47.410 --> 03:48.150
I had been staying up

03:48.150 --> 03:49.579
till dawn writing scripts

03:49.579 --> 03:51.040
with my mentor these days,

03:51.060 --> 03:52.970
so I was available that late at night.

03:52.970 --> 03:54.440
He also promised

03:54.470 --> 03:56.070
to pay me for the trouble.

03:56.579 --> 03:57.910
That's why I went for it.

03:58.360 --> 04:00.650
When I picked you up
at the train station police office,

04:00.650 --> 04:02.510
I was told you're a screenwriter.

04:03.410 --> 04:05.270
You do know how to make up stories.

04:05.400 --> 04:06.840
Are you denying your involvement

04:06.840 --> 04:08.180
to make yourself look innocent?

04:08.180 --> 04:09.020
I'm not making up a story!

04:09.020 --> 04:10.550
Each and every word is true!

04:11.000 --> 04:12.520
I've been in Beijing for a while.

04:12.520 --> 04:14.060
Light has finally shed on my life.

04:14.060 --> 04:15.720
Of course I'll run towards it.

04:16.010 --> 04:17.060
Why would I ruin that

04:17.060 --> 04:18.860
with such a serious illegal act?

04:19.890 --> 04:21.180
Who can testify for you?

04:21.180 --> 04:22.160
Li Xiaobo can!

04:22.240 --> 04:23.840
He was caught too, wasn't he?

04:24.710 --> 04:25.300
Tang,

04:25.390 --> 04:28.110
[Public Security Office]

04:25.930 --> 04:27.040
This time, thank you so much

04:27.040 --> 04:28.250
for making Li Xiaobo tell the truth,

04:28.110 --> 04:32.330
[Reception Room]

04:28.450 --> 04:30.240
so I could clear my name.

04:31.070 --> 04:31.630
I know life is never easy

04:31.630 --> 04:33.220
for dream chasers like you in Beijing.

04:33.220 --> 04:34.330
There is a lot to pay—

04:34.330 --> 04:35.860
life necessities and stuff.

04:35.860 --> 04:37.330
As long as you hang in there
and work hard,

04:37.330 --> 04:39.190
things will keep getting better.

04:39.620 --> 04:40.890
But if you take the wrong path

04:40.890 --> 04:41.920
and jeopardize yourself,

04:41.920 --> 04:42.780
then your dream

04:43.010 --> 04:43.950
will remain just a dream.

04:43.600 --> 04:47.180
[Archives]

04:44.250 --> 04:44.690
Right.

04:45.540 --> 04:46.670
Tang, rest assured.

04:46.810 --> 04:48.010
I'll definitely write

04:48.010 --> 04:49.250
heroes like you

04:49.270 --> 04:50.600
into my future scripts.

04:50.659 --> 04:51.790
Stop flattering me.

04:51.890 --> 04:53.659
You live within my jurisdiction,

04:53.659 --> 04:54.720
so I just did my job.

04:55.220 --> 04:56.220
Go home to eat now.

04:57.630 --> 04:58.370
Thank you!

04:59.180 --> 04:59.780
Off you go.

05:10.090 --> 05:11.060
My apologies.

05:11.190 --> 05:11.630
I'm late.

05:11.630 --> 05:13.690
You won't be late for class, will you?

05:17.390 --> 05:18.070
Freeze!

05:21.980 --> 05:22.910
I-I'll confess.

05:23.220 --> 05:24.920
You're confessing even before I ask?

05:24.920 --> 05:26.510
I'm just hoping for leniency

05:26.510 --> 05:28.040
by showing a good attitude.

05:30.010 --> 05:31.140
Did I tell you to sit?

05:35.180 --> 05:35.920
Confess now.

05:36.130 --> 05:36.640
Yes!

05:37.190 --> 05:39.010
Well, Officer Zhuang,

05:39.600 --> 05:40.500
I did do wrong.

05:41.040 --> 05:43.080
I scalped tickets at the train station.

05:43.080 --> 05:43.780
And then...

05:45.870 --> 05:47.530
Wait. What were you thinking?

05:49.010 --> 05:49.630
How could you

05:49.630 --> 05:50.450
cause trouble again

05:50.450 --> 05:52.310
after just a few days of learning?

05:52.330 --> 05:53.860
I wasn't finished yet.

05:53.870 --> 05:54.830
I didn't really scalp tickets.

05:54.830 --> 05:56.000
I was deceived.

05:56.890 --> 05:57.870
I'm partly at fault, though,

05:57.870 --> 05:59.870
for trying to make some quick money.

06:00.250 --> 06:01.180
You have food and a place to stay.

06:01.180 --> 06:03.040
Why are you so eager to make money?

06:10.180 --> 06:10.930
Are you still thinking

06:10.930 --> 06:12.130
about my lesson fees?

06:13.190 --> 06:14.000
N-No.

06:15.680 --> 06:16.430
Stop eating.

06:21.000 --> 06:22.840
I-I promise

06:22.870 --> 06:24.740
I won't do it again. I won't.

06:25.370 --> 06:27.230
Did you think I'd take your money?

06:28.430 --> 06:30.580
Money you took risks to make?

06:32.400 --> 06:33.890
We lost money in our business.

06:33.890 --> 06:34.890
That was my fault.

06:36.270 --> 06:37.370
I was the reason you couldn't

06:37.370 --> 06:38.240
pay the lesson fees.

06:38.240 --> 06:39.100
I knew

06:39.370 --> 06:40.970
you'd never take that money.

06:41.220 --> 06:42.360
I thought...

06:42.700 --> 06:44.010
after getting the pay,

06:44.159 --> 06:46.020
I'd give it straight to Mr. Zheng.

06:48.300 --> 06:48.740
I knew this thing

06:48.740 --> 06:50.200
must still be on your mind.

06:50.680 --> 06:51.690
Didn't I tell you?

06:51.690 --> 06:53.820
It's normal to lose money in business.

06:54.120 --> 06:54.870
Besides,

06:54.870 --> 06:55.430
that was not

06:55.430 --> 06:56.350
up to you to decide.

06:56.350 --> 06:58.350
I just can't stop thinking about it.

06:59.740 --> 07:00.690
It weighs heavily

07:00.690 --> 07:01.560
on my heart.

07:04.570 --> 07:05.970
Then after today's talk,

07:06.190 --> 07:07.180
let's not bring it up again,

07:07.180 --> 07:07.630
okay?

07:13.930 --> 07:15.480
I know it's absolutely impossible for you

07:15.480 --> 07:16.740
to forget it entirely.

07:17.920 --> 07:18.780
How about this?

07:20.830 --> 07:22.070
When we all sort out

07:22.070 --> 07:22.940
our matters,

07:23.370 --> 07:24.620
I won't stop you from giving me

07:24.620 --> 07:25.480
even 80% of your pay

07:25.480 --> 07:26.740
from writing scripts.

07:27.300 --> 07:28.930
Anyway, you must not strain yourself

07:28.930 --> 07:29.390
to do

07:29.390 --> 07:31.050
such dangerous things again.

07:32.150 --> 07:32.950
That'll work.

07:33.740 --> 07:34.670
It's a good idea.

07:39.720 --> 07:40.159
Dig in.

07:43.130 --> 07:43.600
You too.

07:51.120 --> 07:51.580
Listen,

07:51.890 --> 07:53.090
don't worry about me.

07:53.420 --> 07:54.430
Today, I'm here to tell you

07:54.430 --> 07:55.290
some good news.

07:57.950 --> 07:58.890
I got a job.

07:58.920 --> 07:59.530
Really?

08:00.520 --> 08:01.450
What kind of job?

08:01.560 --> 08:02.630
Mrs. Zheng referred me

08:02.630 --> 08:04.070
for a position as a designer's assistant

08:04.070 --> 08:05.270
in a costume company.

08:05.630 --> 08:06.540
I don't know much about it,

08:06.540 --> 08:08.940
but I'll treat it
as a learning experience.

08:09.250 --> 08:10.450
T-T-That is amazing.

08:11.270 --> 08:12.530
H-How much does it pay?

08:13.450 --> 08:15.580
Nine hundred a month after probation.

08:17.100 --> 08:18.270
Nine hundred?

08:19.610 --> 08:20.610
What do you think?

08:21.630 --> 08:23.180
Incredible. Truly incredible.

08:23.180 --> 08:24.840
T-Then you must try your best.

08:25.000 --> 08:25.330
Well,

08:25.620 --> 08:27.220
I have experience
since I used to be an assisant.

08:27.220 --> 08:28.750
No, I mean I learned my lesson from it.

08:28.750 --> 08:30.240
But I can still share it with you.

08:30.240 --> 08:31.120
I already know every bit

08:31.120 --> 08:32.520
of what you went through.

08:33.440 --> 08:34.169
That's true.

08:34.860 --> 08:35.600
You're amazing,

08:35.600 --> 08:37.330
and you can do everything well.

08:38.120 --> 08:39.980
Let this be an early celebration.

08:40.500 --> 08:41.830
I wish you every success

08:42.320 --> 08:44.320
in your first job, Designer Zhuang!

08:45.190 --> 08:45.850
To success!

08:52.100 --> 08:54.410
Why must you bring up the past?

08:54.410 --> 08:55.390
W-Who are you?

08:58.000 --> 08:59.330
What are you doing here?

09:02.620 --> 09:03.680
I'm talking to you!

09:06.740 --> 09:07.600
Did you miss me?

09:09.750 --> 09:10.480
I'm back,

09:11.080 --> 09:13.400
buddies!

09:14.460 --> 09:15.440
Cao?

09:15.500 --> 09:16.420
Heretic Cao?

09:16.620 --> 09:18.220
-You... You little punk!
-Zongbao.

09:18.220 --> 09:18.740
Liangliang!

09:18.740 --> 09:20.320
-Why are you back?
-Liangliang, Liangliang!

09:20.320 --> 09:20.910
Coming!

09:20.910 --> 09:21.290
Shengli.

09:21.290 --> 09:21.700
What?

09:21.870 --> 09:23.450
What were you doing?

09:23.530 --> 09:24.480
Look who's back!

09:24.480 --> 09:25.500
Where have you been?

09:25.500 --> 09:26.240
I just spent

09:26.250 --> 09:27.290
the previous few days outside

09:27.290 --> 09:28.890
reflecting on my life and...

09:29.130 --> 09:29.860
Liangliang.

09:31.220 --> 09:31.950
I missed you.

09:38.100 --> 09:39.880
I really missed you guys.

09:40.790 --> 09:41.360
Liangliang,

09:41.360 --> 09:42.290
I missed you lot.

09:42.480 --> 09:43.100
I missed you lot.

09:43.100 --> 09:43.560
Wait.

09:43.820 --> 09:45.950
W-Where did your hair go?

09:46.120 --> 09:48.340
It was cut off and gone

09:48.410 --> 09:49.120
with my dignity

09:49.120 --> 09:50.180
and perseverance.

09:50.480 --> 09:51.220
Do I look good?

09:51.220 --> 09:52.240
You had dignity?

09:52.240 --> 09:53.200
Grab weapons!

09:53.910 --> 09:54.410
No!

10:07.440 --> 10:09.170
Your job's also so exhausting?

10:09.290 --> 10:11.390
Your schedule is almost as crazy as mine.

10:11.390 --> 10:12.050
Say no more.

10:12.750 --> 10:13.890
Now I finally realize

10:13.890 --> 10:15.350
how hard it's been for you.

10:17.860 --> 10:18.390
Oh right.

10:19.370 --> 10:20.410
You are well-read.

10:20.410 --> 10:21.810
Can you make a list for me?

10:22.100 --> 10:22.630
Sure.

10:22.790 --> 10:23.790
What kind of list?

10:23.860 --> 10:25.120
Just a list of books

10:25.120 --> 10:26.460
on design, art, and literature.

10:26.460 --> 10:27.060
Anything.

10:27.120 --> 10:29.050
You need to read these books
to do your job

10:29.050 --> 10:30.240
as a designer's assistant?

10:30.240 --> 10:31.170
Tell me about it.

10:32.010 --> 10:33.370
Up till now, I even haven't met

10:33.370 --> 10:34.300
with Ms. Yue yet.

10:35.290 --> 10:37.600
She's quite strange, indeed.

10:38.250 --> 10:39.180
If Ms. Yue

10:39.550 --> 10:41.010
somehow gets together

10:41.010 --> 10:41.960
with Mr. He,

10:42.080 --> 10:43.460
won't it be fun?

10:43.550 --> 10:45.460
You just love the drama, don't you?

10:45.460 --> 10:47.010
No, I'm just being curious.

10:47.720 --> 10:48.530
Don't worry.

10:48.670 --> 10:49.450
I promise

10:49.630 --> 10:51.570
to draw on all my knowledge and abilities

10:51.570 --> 10:52.470
to make a clear

10:52.500 --> 10:53.750
and thorough list for you.

10:53.750 --> 10:56.350
Thank you then,
Mr. Xu the great screenwriter.

10:56.750 --> 10:57.680
You're welcome.

10:58.420 --> 10:59.300
As it happens,

10:59.480 --> 11:00.960
I need a favor from you too.

11:01.360 --> 11:01.960
What is it?

11:04.010 --> 11:04.410
A character

11:04.410 --> 11:06.120
in the script that Mr. He is writing

11:06.120 --> 11:07.600
is a tailor.

11:07.860 --> 11:09.580
He doesn't think my portrayal of it
is accurate enough.

11:09.580 --> 11:11.550
I only know a little bit
about this profession.

11:11.550 --> 11:12.630
My portrayal of it is indeed

11:12.630 --> 11:13.890
distant with reality.

11:14.390 --> 11:15.350
That's easy.

11:15.480 --> 11:16.740
You can consult my mom.

11:18.000 --> 11:18.950
N-no need.

11:19.130 --> 11:20.530
R-Really, no. I-I-I...

11:20.530 --> 11:21.930
I can just interview you.

11:23.500 --> 11:24.270
Or you can

11:24.270 --> 11:25.890
interview your mother in my stead.

11:25.890 --> 11:26.890
That's no good.

11:27.290 --> 11:28.790
You need a real tailor's opnion.

11:28.790 --> 11:29.650
My mom is a professional.

11:29.650 --> 11:30.290
I'm not.

11:33.620 --> 11:35.200
T-Then fine.

11:35.650 --> 11:36.720
I'll write your mother

11:36.720 --> 11:37.460
a letter later.

11:37.460 --> 11:38.720
Why write her a letter?

11:39.000 --> 11:40.400
Isn't there a phone here?

11:43.000 --> 11:44.400
You can call her anytime.

11:50.030 --> 11:50.910
Why don't you do it now?

11:50.910 --> 11:51.900
N-No, not now.

11:52.200 --> 11:53.550
I need to make a draft first.

11:53.550 --> 11:54.290
No, not a draft.

11:54.290 --> 11:55.890
I must make an interview outline

11:55.890 --> 11:56.630
first.

11:59.860 --> 12:01.700
M- Making an interview outline

12:01.740 --> 12:02.940
is perfectly normal.

12:12.240 --> 12:13.970
Why did you drink so much again?

12:14.500 --> 12:15.100
Take this.

12:29.360 --> 12:30.000
Zhuang.

12:33.390 --> 12:34.050
Do you think

12:34.790 --> 12:36.200
I'm a good actress?

12:36.650 --> 12:37.650
Of course you are.

12:37.950 --> 12:39.210
Do you even need to ask?

12:41.010 --> 12:43.270
Mr. Chu said the same thing.

12:44.860 --> 12:46.280
You drank with him again?

12:46.720 --> 12:48.320
It was practically an honor.

12:49.940 --> 12:50.940
How could I not go?

12:54.370 --> 12:54.770
You've

12:54.770 --> 12:56.360
drunk with him so many times.

12:56.360 --> 12:57.890
Have you secured any roles?

12:58.440 --> 13:00.040
He didn't confirm anything.

13:02.980 --> 13:04.710
If you keep drinking like this,

13:04.790 --> 13:06.240
your health will be ruined.

13:06.240 --> 13:07.970
I don't want to drink like this.

13:10.460 --> 13:12.060
But time is all I have.

13:13.910 --> 13:15.910
Trading time for an opportunity...

13:17.030 --> 13:17.890
is worthwhile.

13:37.100 --> 13:37.830
What now?

13:41.290 --> 13:41.630
I...

13:42.000 --> 13:44.010
My throat feels a bit tight.

13:44.580 --> 13:53.550
[Registration Room]

13:45.360 --> 13:47.760
It's not like you're going to
sing to my mom.

13:49.130 --> 13:49.860
Then let's quit.

13:49.860 --> 13:50.990
No, please call her.

13:51.980 --> 13:52.310
Do it.

13:54.200 --> 13:54.700
You sure?

13:54.700 --> 13:55.120
Yes.

14:12.010 --> 14:12.870
How about we...

14:14.240 --> 14:14.860
Hey, Mom.

14:17.500 --> 14:19.650
I'm calling for what I told you yesterday.

14:19.650 --> 14:21.050
Shengli will talk to you.

14:21.050 --> 14:22.380
Chat with her a bit more.

14:22.400 --> 14:23.930
Phone calls are expensive.

14:24.500 --> 14:24.900
Hurry.

14:30.300 --> 14:31.160
Hello, auntie.

14:31.740 --> 14:32.400
Yes, right.

14:33.130 --> 14:34.190
This is Xu Shengli.

14:34.720 --> 14:35.520
Exactly, yes.

14:36.240 --> 14:37.890
How have you been, auntie?

14:39.790 --> 14:40.880
That's good.

14:41.890 --> 14:42.750
Zhuang Zhuang?

14:43.320 --> 14:45.650
Learning to sing
does take a lot out of her,

14:46.510 --> 14:48.040
but she sings beautifully.

14:48.080 --> 14:50.140
Everyone here loves to hear her sing.

14:50.620 --> 14:52.080
She sings for us every day.

14:52.180 --> 14:53.460
When she sings too much,

14:53.460 --> 14:54.520
s-she gets hungry.

14:54.650 --> 14:56.310
Her meals are going fine, too.

14:56.320 --> 14:57.350
She eats a lot.

14:57.380 --> 14:58.310
Get to the point.

14:58.940 --> 14:59.980
Just don't worry.

15:02.170 --> 15:02.690
Yes.

15:02.940 --> 15:04.290
I was just talking to her about it.

15:04.290 --> 15:04.840
I said,

15:05.080 --> 15:05.720
I must

15:05.740 --> 15:07.600
visit Wenzhou if there is a chance,

15:07.600 --> 15:10.260
for the wonderful landscapes there.

15:10.480 --> 15:11.260
There is a...

15:11.280 --> 15:12.410
What mountain is it?

15:12.820 --> 15:13.550
Right!

15:13.570 --> 15:14.770
That exact mountain!

15:15.810 --> 15:16.410
Yes.

15:16.450 --> 15:18.070
What a place of stunning scenery,
fresh air,

15:18.070 --> 15:19.200
and perfect humidity.

15:19.200 --> 15:20.800
It's too dry here in Beijing.

15:23.410 --> 15:24.270
My parents?

15:24.740 --> 15:25.940
They are doing quite well.

15:24.910 --> 15:25.600
[List of Questions]

15:25.620 --> 15:26.450
[People all like Dacron
and knickerbockers]

15:25.990 --> 15:26.770
They are both in Shandong.

15:26.470 --> 15:27.490
[Which kind of fabric
do people order most from your shop?]

15:27.510 --> 15:29.090
[What do customers especially care about
when they choose fabrics?]

15:28.220 --> 15:29.540
They're also in good health.

15:29.540 --> 15:31.140
Just don't worry, auntie.

15:33.010 --> 15:34.620
Well, I take good care of her.

15:34.750 --> 15:35.440
Everyone here

15:35.440 --> 15:36.700
takes good care of her.

15:37.240 --> 15:37.580
Right.

15:37.580 --> 15:38.890
That's mainly because she is nice

15:38.890 --> 15:40.090
to everyone here too.

15:40.250 --> 15:41.580
Yes, just be assured.

15:44.700 --> 15:46.010
Enough. Cut to the chase.

15:46.010 --> 15:47.390
I-I do have a question.

15:47.390 --> 15:47.950
Well,

15:48.010 --> 15:49.170
auntie, may I ask something?

15:49.170 --> 15:50.590
Suppose you meet

15:50.770 --> 15:52.130
an extremely difficult client

15:52.130 --> 15:53.300
during

15:53.500 --> 15:54.200
the sales process,

15:54.200 --> 15:55.440
then

15:55.630 --> 15:56.650
h-how would you

15:56.670 --> 15:57.620
usually

15:57.670 --> 15:58.870
decline them?

16:00.050 --> 16:01.540
Auntie, wait a second.

16:01.650 --> 16:02.580
I'll take notes.

16:05.680 --> 16:06.680
Go ahead, please.

16:08.010 --> 16:12.530
[Registration Room]

16:34.910 --> 16:37.670
You've been laughing since yesterday.

16:38.860 --> 16:39.620
You asked my mom

16:39.620 --> 16:41.080
what she had for dinner the night before.

16:41.080 --> 16:42.290
What were you thinking?

16:42.290 --> 16:43.080
I was just showing care

16:43.080 --> 16:44.790
for her on your behalf, wasn't I?

16:44.790 --> 16:45.730
You have no idea.

16:46.000 --> 16:47.480
Nowadays, many older family members

16:47.480 --> 16:48.620
at home would skip dinner

16:48.620 --> 16:49.680
just to save money.

16:49.910 --> 16:50.810
That's no good.

16:53.150 --> 16:54.810
So you did plan to ask her that.

16:55.740 --> 16:56.870
O-Of course.

16:58.670 --> 16:59.550
Then, did that call

16:59.550 --> 17:01.720
solve the problem you met
in writing the script?

17:01.720 --> 17:02.860
It gave me huge help.

17:02.960 --> 17:03.270
Listen,

17:03.270 --> 17:04.109
next time I see your mother,

17:04.109 --> 17:05.510
I must thank her properly.

17:05.510 --> 17:06.980
You should first thank her daughter

17:06.980 --> 17:07.660
properly.

17:07.880 --> 17:08.880
That's a must.

17:09.400 --> 17:10.740
Today, I'll go ask Mr. He

17:10.750 --> 17:11.569
for a permission

17:11.569 --> 17:13.910
to add a special thanks in the script

17:14.200 --> 17:16.660
to the beautiful and kind
Ms. Zhuang Zhuang.

17:18.849 --> 17:19.900
Why don't you just change

17:19.900 --> 17:21.069
the character's name

17:21.069 --> 17:21.810
to mine?

17:22.109 --> 17:22.550
No way.

17:23.030 --> 17:24.069
N-Not a chance.

17:24.500 --> 17:25.010
Why?

17:25.569 --> 17:27.500
She and her love in the script
end up splitting up.

17:27.500 --> 17:28.160
It's a jinx.

17:37.660 --> 17:38.060
You...

17:39.180 --> 17:40.200
L-Let me go get you

17:40.200 --> 17:40.850
that list.

17:53.720 --> 17:54.450
Not this one.

17:57.050 --> 17:57.660
Here it is.

17:58.720 --> 17:59.470
Take a look.

18:00.350 --> 18:01.500
I have the ones

18:01.500 --> 18:02.500
with checkmarks.

18:02.770 --> 18:05.050
You'll have to find the rest
in the library.

18:05.050 --> 18:06.350
Let me know when you go there.

18:06.350 --> 18:08.950
These many books are too heavy
for you to carry.

18:11.670 --> 18:13.200
Can't I borrow one at a time?

18:14.850 --> 18:15.850
That's an option.

18:16.310 --> 18:17.510
How brilliant of you.

18:18.950 --> 18:20.640
Thanks, Mr. Xu the great screenwriter.

18:20.640 --> 18:21.400
No problem.

18:32.510 --> 18:33.400
Why is there no one here today?

18:33.400 --> 18:34.080
Where are they?

18:34.080 --> 18:34.810
Liangliang.

18:35.810 --> 18:37.220
The kitchen drain is clogged.

18:37.220 --> 18:39.010
Mr. Tao is having a plumper fix it.

18:39.010 --> 18:39.540
All done.

18:39.960 --> 18:40.900
It's unclogged now.

18:40.900 --> 18:41.390
Good.

18:41.420 --> 18:42.950
Let me sweep this up for you.

18:43.210 --> 18:44.480
Thank you.

18:44.680 --> 18:45.350
Thanks.

18:46.010 --> 18:46.540
Alright.

18:48.570 --> 18:48.900
Done.

18:49.680 --> 18:50.660
Thanks for your hard work.

18:50.660 --> 18:51.190
Anytime.

18:51.350 --> 18:51.680
Okay.

18:52.110 --> 18:53.170
Let me walk you out.

18:53.640 --> 18:54.170
Alright.

18:54.750 --> 18:55.140
Okay.

18:55.240 --> 18:55.550
I-I'll put it here.

18:55.550 --> 18:56.090
Thanks for the hard work.

18:56.090 --> 18:57.690
Alright, let me walk you out.

18:57.700 --> 18:58.500
Thanks again.

18:59.480 --> 19:00.480
No need to see me off.

19:00.480 --> 19:01.510
-Okay.
-Zongbao!

19:03.960 --> 19:05.290
What brings you to our place?

19:05.290 --> 19:06.290
This is our place.

19:06.400 --> 19:07.700
I-I didn't know.

19:07.850 --> 19:08.780
You didn't know?

19:09.350 --> 19:11.080
I hired him to fix the plumbing.

19:13.160 --> 19:13.480
Dad,

19:13.530 --> 19:14.110
he's the man

19:14.110 --> 19:15.370
I often told you about,

19:15.770 --> 19:16.790
who treated me

19:16.880 --> 19:18.180
very nicely in the hostel,

19:18.180 --> 19:19.240
named Guo Zongbao.

19:19.680 --> 19:20.680
It is him exactly.

19:20.720 --> 19:22.070
He's not a plumber.

19:22.460 --> 19:23.060
Uncle Tao.

19:24.700 --> 19:25.500
He's an actor.

19:26.660 --> 19:28.980
Doing research by living the life,
aren't you?

19:28.980 --> 19:30.190
W-What a coincidence.

19:30.190 --> 19:31.320
So random to run into

19:30.440 --> 19:33.500
[Welcome]

19:31.350 --> 19:32.720
a friend of yours, Liangliang.

19:32.720 --> 19:34.460
I just stewed a pot of pork shoulder.

19:34.460 --> 19:36.010
How about I cook a few more dishes?

19:36.010 --> 19:37.200
Everyone stay for a meal.

19:37.200 --> 19:38.070
Uncle Tao...

19:38.070 --> 19:38.730
Just stay.

19:38.900 --> 19:40.330
My dad is a great cook.

19:40.480 --> 19:41.570
He makes amazing

19:41.570 --> 19:42.160
pork shoulder.

19:42.160 --> 19:42.550
Come on.

19:42.550 --> 19:43.700
I-I have to leave.

19:45.570 --> 19:46.830
Let my dad cook for you.

19:47.160 --> 19:48.270
-Liangliang...
-Say no more.

19:48.270 --> 19:49.670
Nothing needs to be said.

19:49.920 --> 19:50.720
I understand.

19:51.830 --> 19:52.890
A drink at my place?

19:54.920 --> 19:55.720
I-I should...

19:57.550 --> 19:59.530
-Come on, Zongbao!
-Fine, okay.

20:03.250 --> 20:05.530
Repairing range hoods!

20:04.680 --> 20:09.350
[Professional Repair
of All Home Appliances]

20:05.560 --> 20:08.220
Repairing range hoods!

20:08.440 --> 20:10.730
Unclogging drains!

20:10.890 --> 20:15.660
[Professional Repair
of All Home Appliances]

20:12.420 --> 20:14.590
Repairing range hoods!

20:14.590 --> 20:15.320
Liangliang.

20:15.920 --> 20:16.810
Well,

20:17.330 --> 20:19.250
I need to park the bike

20:19.310 --> 20:20.250
over there.

20:20.570 --> 20:22.330
I'm not going any further this way.

20:22.330 --> 20:23.200
I'll park the bike first

20:23.200 --> 20:28.550
[Professional Repair
of All Home Appliances]

20:23.250 --> 20:24.890
and then go home.

20:25.010 --> 20:26.090
You should've said it earlier,

20:26.090 --> 20:27.480
so you didn't have to
walk such a long way with me.

20:27.480 --> 20:28.080
It's okay.

20:28.790 --> 20:29.520
Easy does it.

20:30.270 --> 20:31.920
Don't go to work again.

20:32.030 --> 20:33.230
Listen, Liangliang,

20:34.090 --> 20:35.400
please don't tell anyone

20:35.400 --> 20:36.660
what happened today.

20:37.350 --> 20:38.020
I know.

20:38.510 --> 20:40.360
Nobody will know it

20:40.610 --> 20:41.680
if we both keep it secret.

20:41.680 --> 20:44.480
You're just experiencing real life
for your acting.

20:44.480 --> 20:46.010
Zongbao, I have a question.

20:46.640 --> 20:48.140
Back in the hostel,

20:48.770 --> 20:50.970
you told us stories from your hometown.

20:51.960 --> 20:52.960
Are they all true?

20:53.160 --> 20:53.960
Yes, all true.

20:54.000 --> 20:55.460
You do have a wife

20:55.550 --> 20:56.610
and a child, right?

20:58.010 --> 20:59.410
Yes, I have photos.

20:59.510 --> 21:00.170
Okay, okay.

21:00.510 --> 21:01.850
As long as they're all true.

21:01.850 --> 21:03.250
Don't make them up as part

21:03.330 --> 21:04.510
of your preparation for acting.

21:04.510 --> 21:05.700
Raising a family is a serious matter.

21:05.700 --> 21:07.030
You must want a beating.

21:07.720 --> 21:08.380
I have to go.

21:08.810 --> 21:09.610
Go home early.

21:09.660 --> 21:10.550
Sure, sure.

21:12.850 --> 21:13.520
Off I go.

21:14.220 --> 21:15.350
I'll head home soon.

21:15.740 --> 21:16.980
Just return the bike.

21:17.010 --> 21:18.550
Don't go to work again.

21:19.010 --> 21:19.870
Got it. I won't.

21:21.500 --> 21:21.960
Go home.

21:29.270 --> 21:32.290
-Repairing range hoods!
-Look at that.

21:32.680 --> 21:35.000
Unclogging drains!

21:36.530 --> 21:37.390
Zhuang Zhuang.

21:37.400 --> 21:38.590
How are things at Ms. Yue's office

21:38.590 --> 21:39.290
lately?

21:39.440 --> 21:40.170
Pretty good.

21:41.500 --> 21:42.060
My friend

21:42.090 --> 21:42.830
told me Ms. Yue has

21:42.830 --> 21:43.960
an odd disposition.

21:44.010 --> 21:44.850
Whatever she says to you,

21:44.850 --> 21:46.110
don't take it to heart.

21:46.460 --> 21:47.790
I'm practically an amateur.

21:47.790 --> 21:48.590
So, I'm taking

21:49.030 --> 21:50.600
this time to study hard

21:50.920 --> 21:51.920
and get fully prepared.

21:51.920 --> 21:52.770
I'm back!

21:53.750 --> 21:54.920
-Mr. Zheng.
-Mrs. Zheng,

21:54.920 --> 21:55.980
is Zhuang Zhuang here?

21:55.980 --> 21:56.640
Yes, she is.

21:57.270 --> 21:59.270
-She arrived early.
-Already here?

21:59.270 --> 22:00.500
Let me tell you something.

22:00.500 --> 22:00.960
Come on.

22:00.960 --> 22:01.570
Sit down first.

22:01.570 --> 22:02.180
Okay.

22:02.550 --> 22:04.110
What is it? You seem happy.

22:05.400 --> 22:06.330
Tomorrow night,

22:06.380 --> 22:07.510
there will be a show,

22:07.900 --> 22:09.320
including

22:09.640 --> 22:10.690
a female quartet.

22:10.850 --> 22:11.880
But now, all of a sudden,

22:11.880 --> 22:12.880
one of the singers

22:13.130 --> 22:13.990
has fallen sick

22:14.090 --> 22:15.150
and cannot make it.

22:15.500 --> 22:17.500
I was asked to find someone
to replace her.

22:17.500 --> 22:18.300
I'm wondering

22:18.440 --> 22:20.040
if you'd like to give it a try.

22:20.460 --> 22:21.450
Yes, I'd love to!

22:21.480 --> 22:22.290
-No, no.
-Of course I'd love to!

22:22.290 --> 22:22.890
No, no way.

22:22.980 --> 22:23.780
I object to it.

22:24.160 --> 22:25.110
For what reason?

22:25.220 --> 22:25.880
How can Zhuang Zhuang

22:25.880 --> 22:27.310
be someone's replacement?

22:27.310 --> 22:27.810
That won't do.

22:27.810 --> 22:28.240
It's not like that.

22:28.240 --> 22:28.880
It is. You...

22:28.880 --> 22:30.070
Please hear me out.

22:30.640 --> 22:32.100
The troupe is recruiting right now.

22:32.100 --> 22:34.430
If Zhuang Zhuang performs well this time,

22:34.590 --> 22:35.400
there will be tons

22:35.400 --> 22:37.600
of opportunities for her in the future.

22:37.900 --> 22:40.160
Mrs. Zheng, I want to go.
I'd love to do it.

22:40.400 --> 22:41.110
Fine.

22:41.140 --> 22:42.940
Whatever Zhuang Zhuang wants to do.

22:42.940 --> 22:43.970
Break a leg!

22:45.170 --> 22:46.370
Thank you, Mr. Zheng.

22:46.600 --> 22:47.790
It's nothing.

22:49.200 --> 22:51.400
Master, how have your eyes been lately?

22:52.590 --> 22:53.850
Sometimes good, and sometimes bad.

22:53.850 --> 22:55.150
Don't worry about me.

22:55.740 --> 22:57.720
For your good-looking friend's

22:57.770 --> 22:58.900
first performance,

22:59.460 --> 23:01.060
you must dress up nicely.

23:13.960 --> 23:14.960
Now, you look...

23:15.900 --> 23:17.430
a bit like me back in the day.

23:19.510 --> 23:20.530
Years ago,

23:20.550 --> 23:22.310
a director told me

23:23.460 --> 23:24.720
that in the whole crew,

23:24.850 --> 23:26.110
including the actors,

23:26.330 --> 23:28.990
the most handsome one was me,
the screenwriter.

23:29.830 --> 23:31.200
The director must have had a problem

23:31.200 --> 23:32.130
with the actors.

23:32.220 --> 23:33.440
If you were the best-looking one,

23:33.440 --> 23:34.590
the actors must look terrible, right?

23:34.590 --> 23:35.660
What's that gibberish?

23:35.660 --> 23:37.270
The suit. Mind the suit!

23:37.400 --> 23:38.470
Right, right.

23:43.720 --> 23:46.100
I wore this about ten years ago

23:46.720 --> 23:48.130
when I attended

23:48.220 --> 23:50.550
the premiere of my work
for the first time.

23:51.940 --> 23:53.270
It's been over a decade.

23:54.240 --> 23:55.550
I don't have a son,

23:57.920 --> 23:58.900
so lucky you.

24:04.790 --> 24:05.250
Thanks.

24:24.440 --> 24:27.100
[Please line up to board
and let passengers off first]

24:36.670 --> 24:45.170
[The Voice of Classics]

24:37.330 --> 24:41.480
Wild geese are flying south.

24:41.770 --> 24:45.940
Wild geese are flying south.

24:46.480 --> 24:54.220
The cries of wild geese break my heart.

24:54.850 --> 24:59.940
Though you're only leaving today,

25:00.900 --> 25:06.710
I am already yearning for your return
in spring.

25:06.920 --> 25:14.570
I am already yearning for your return
in spring.

25:15.680 --> 25:19.610
After you depart today,

25:19.960 --> 25:25.270
do come back in spring.

25:26.110 --> 25:28.700
I long for your return.

25:30.250 --> 25:35.920
Don't shatter my heart.

25:37.510 --> 25:45.310
Don't shatter my heart.

25:45.920 --> 25:55.550
I await your return in spring.

25:46.170 --> 25:51.530
[The Voice of Classics]

25:56.380 --> 26:00.750
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

26:02.620 --> 26:06.040
[The Voice of Classics]

26:06.300 --> 26:10.200
[The Voice of Classics by the Art Troupe]

26:07.660 --> 26:09.750
This theater is no good.

26:10.220 --> 26:14.810
[In full bloom in Beiyin Concert Hall]

26:10.310 --> 26:11.220
They won't let friends

26:11.220 --> 26:12.820
and relatives go backstage.

26:12.830 --> 26:14.770
H-How do we present these flowers
to Zhuang?

26:14.770 --> 26:16.000
Look how antsy Shengli is.

26:16.000 --> 26:17.010
I'm not antsy at all.

26:17.010 --> 26:18.340
We'll see her soon.

26:18.530 --> 26:19.770
Zhuang Zhuang is a substitute.

26:19.770 --> 26:20.640
It makes sense

26:20.640 --> 26:21.250
that they won't let us in.

26:21.250 --> 26:22.580
She'll be out here soon.

26:25.460 --> 26:26.250
Zhuang Zhuang is out now.

26:26.250 --> 26:27.110
Zhuang Zhuang!

26:27.380 --> 26:28.240
Zhuang Zhuang!

26:28.460 --> 26:28.900
Zhuang!

26:28.900 --> 26:29.270
Zhuang Zhuang.

26:29.270 --> 26:30.310
-Wait a sec!
-Here!

26:30.310 --> 26:31.320
Great work today.

26:31.380 --> 26:32.270
Cheer her on, shall we?

26:32.270 --> 26:33.190
Sure, let's cheer her on.

26:33.190 --> 26:35.000
-Zhuang Zhuang!
-Zhuang Zhuang!

26:35.000 --> 26:36.060
Congratulations.

26:36.140 --> 26:36.960
Thanks.

26:36.960 --> 26:37.820
Zhuang Zhuang!

26:38.570 --> 26:40.610
-Zhuang Zhuang!
-Zhuang Zhuang!

26:40.720 --> 26:41.920
How about we take a photo?

26:41.920 --> 26:46.520
[Beiyin Concert Hall]

26:42.220 --> 26:43.270
Yes, let's take a photo.

26:43.270 --> 26:43.900
That guy...

26:43.900 --> 26:44.680
has a camera, so he must know

26:44.680 --> 26:45.180
how to take photos.

26:45.180 --> 26:46.510
-That one.
-Hey, buddy!

26:46.570 --> 26:48.160
I could hear you sing even outside.

26:48.160 --> 26:49.690
Could you take a photo of us?

26:49.740 --> 26:50.240
Sure.

26:50.420 --> 26:51.470
Thank you so much.

26:51.510 --> 26:52.380
Thanks for the help.

26:52.380 --> 26:53.530
Get the banner above in the frame too.

26:53.530 --> 26:54.240
This banner?

26:53.820 --> 26:58.090
[Beiyin Concert Hall]

26:54.250 --> 26:54.780
Exactly.

26:55.350 --> 26:55.950
Thank you.

26:56.000 --> 26:56.920
This spot is good.

26:56.920 --> 26:57.810
Mr. Xu, hurry.

26:57.810 --> 26:59.590
-D-Don't forget the banner.
-Come over now.

26:59.590 --> 27:00.200
He's waiting.

27:00.200 --> 27:01.290
Come here quickly, Liangliang!

27:01.290 --> 27:02.200
Come on.

27:02.290 --> 27:02.890
Get ready.

27:05.480 --> 27:06.930
Look here, everyone.

27:06.980 --> 27:08.380
Keep your smiles on.

27:08.590 --> 27:11.590
Alright. Three, two, one!

27:11.830 --> 27:12.240
Done.

27:12.290 --> 27:12.640
Great.

27:12.640 --> 27:13.140
Thank you.

27:13.140 --> 27:13.930
Many thanks.

27:14.440 --> 27:14.900
What now?

27:14.900 --> 27:15.760
Get back there.

27:15.790 --> 27:17.290
You and John should take a photo.

27:17.290 --> 27:18.570
-Just go.
-Let's get a photo of you two.

27:18.570 --> 27:19.850
Hurry.

27:20.180 --> 27:21.960
Don't be shy. Get closer.

27:22.000 --> 27:23.220
Saving that space for someone
to stand between you, huh?

27:23.220 --> 27:23.880
Put on a smile!

27:23.880 --> 27:25.850
I-Is someone going to stand between you?

27:25.850 --> 27:26.650
Right. Closer

27:26.770 --> 27:27.570
to each other.

27:28.510 --> 27:29.220
Smile!

27:31.000 --> 27:31.530
What are you doing?

27:31.530 --> 27:32.460
Guys, catch him!

27:32.530 --> 27:34.460
What kind of motorcyclist are you?

27:38.220 --> 27:39.420
-Is that guy blind or what?
-Where did you get hurt?

27:39.420 --> 27:39.920
Shengli!

27:39.920 --> 27:40.500
Where did you get hit?

27:40.500 --> 27:41.090
The leg or the foot?

27:41.090 --> 27:42.660
Don't move me or touch it.

27:43.570 --> 27:44.190
Shengli,

27:44.380 --> 27:45.110
are you okay?

27:45.420 --> 27:46.240
That motorcyclist

27:46.240 --> 27:47.700
seemed to be Kang Shunyin.

27:47.700 --> 27:48.500
Kang Shunyin?

27:49.330 --> 27:51.220
-Let's take him to the hospital now.
-Hurry.

27:51.220 --> 27:53.080
-To the hospital.
-Hurry, get up.

27:53.460 --> 27:54.070
Don't put weight on your foot.

27:54.070 --> 27:54.710
Hop up.

27:54.900 --> 27:55.330
Careful.

27:55.330 --> 27:56.290
A bit higher up the back.

27:56.290 --> 27:56.820
Let's go.

27:59.720 --> 28:00.350
Nice and slow.

28:00.350 --> 28:01.600
It hurts!

28:01.790 --> 28:02.290
Hurry.

28:02.290 --> 28:03.660
Put his feet on the bed.

28:03.750 --> 28:06.350
-Such suffering for Xu.
-This is the good foot.

28:06.530 --> 28:08.530
Slowly. Don't let it get hurt again.

28:09.050 --> 28:10.250
-Come on.
-Lean back.

28:10.920 --> 28:12.250
Let's save a beautiful memory.

28:12.250 --> 28:13.180
One, two, three!

28:13.380 --> 28:14.550
Zongbao, get closer to him.

28:14.550 --> 28:15.870
Don't waste the film.

28:15.960 --> 28:17.880
-Get that foot in the frame.
-One more photo, with the foot in.

28:17.880 --> 28:18.810
One, two, three!

28:20.460 --> 28:20.860
Done.

28:21.090 --> 28:21.590
All done.

28:21.590 --> 28:22.120
Alright.

28:22.790 --> 28:23.770
Today, if it hadn't been for

28:23.770 --> 28:24.810
my leather shoes and jeans

28:24.810 --> 28:25.810
restraining me from taking

28:25.810 --> 28:27.400
big steps, I would've caught that guy!

28:27.400 --> 28:28.380
If that's what you're saying,

28:28.380 --> 28:29.610
I'd say it happened so suddenly

28:29.610 --> 28:30.180
that it caught me off guard.

28:30.180 --> 28:31.310
Otherwise, I could've pulled him down

28:31.310 --> 28:32.080
before you went after him, right?

28:32.080 --> 28:34.160
I'm telling you, that guy is brutal,

28:34.240 --> 28:34.660
isn't he?

28:34.660 --> 28:35.900
Look what he did to Shengli.

28:35.900 --> 28:37.090
-Xu Shengli.
-Officer Tang.

28:37.090 --> 28:37.890
Officer Tang.

28:38.290 --> 28:38.790
Officer Tang.

28:38.790 --> 28:39.990
Is your foot alright?

28:40.960 --> 28:41.480
Yes,

28:41.750 --> 28:42.350
it's fine.

28:43.240 --> 28:44.100
I just found out

28:44.270 --> 28:44.900
that Kang Shunyin

28:44.900 --> 28:46.350
had attacked more than once.

28:46.350 --> 28:48.080
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

28:49.180 --> 28:50.310
That was because...

28:52.050 --> 28:53.710
we didn't want to trouble you.

28:54.280 --> 28:56.080
A sensible citizen, aren't you?

28:56.530 --> 28:58.030
Later, I'll go to the pricinct

28:58.030 --> 28:59.290
to report this matter.

28:59.750 --> 29:01.950
His behavior this time was outrageous.

29:02.140 --> 29:03.940
We will definitely take action.

29:05.350 --> 29:06.040
From now on,

29:06.180 --> 29:06.790
he won't disturb

29:06.790 --> 29:07.750
your life anymore.

29:07.750 --> 29:08.550
Rest assured.

29:08.980 --> 29:10.380
Thank you, Officer Tang.

29:11.270 --> 29:12.310
It's not easy for a girl to make

29:12.310 --> 29:13.440
a living in Beijing.

29:13.530 --> 29:14.640
But don't fret if anything happens.

29:14.640 --> 29:15.880
Just turn to the police.

29:15.880 --> 29:16.420
Got it?

29:17.240 --> 29:17.640
Got it.

29:18.420 --> 29:18.950
Alright.

29:19.380 --> 29:20.400
Take good care of him.

29:20.400 --> 29:20.960
I'm leaving then.

29:20.960 --> 29:21.420
Thank you.

29:21.420 --> 29:22.110
Goodbye, Officer Tang.

29:22.110 --> 29:22.760
Take care.

29:22.940 --> 29:24.200
Sorry for the trouble.

29:24.290 --> 29:25.420
It's also not easy for a young man

29:25.420 --> 29:26.950
to make a living in Beijing.

29:30.380 --> 29:31.240
Does it hurt?

29:32.810 --> 29:33.410
Not at all.

29:33.790 --> 29:35.050
It doesn't hurt at all.

29:36.770 --> 29:38.010
He was howling in pain just now,

29:38.010 --> 29:39.810
and he's all fine at this moment.

29:41.850 --> 29:43.460
Don't take their nonsense seriously.

29:43.460 --> 29:44.720
I'm really not in pain.

29:52.310 --> 29:53.310
It's all my fault.

29:53.900 --> 29:54.550
How are you going

29:54.550 --> 29:56.220
to write scripts
when you're injured like this?

29:56.220 --> 29:58.200
I-I don't write with my feet.

29:58.240 --> 29:59.000
I'm really fine.

29:59.000 --> 29:59.930
Look at my hands.

29:59.940 --> 30:01.600
Perfectly fine, aren't they?

30:03.850 --> 30:05.180
It really doesn't hurt.

30:07.240 --> 30:08.530
It doesn't. Look.

30:09.680 --> 30:10.610
I'm really fine.

30:38.310 --> 30:39.440
Take your medicine.

30:58.830 --> 31:00.830
Can't you let me pose properly
for a photo?

31:00.830 --> 31:02.490
You look great no matter what.

31:03.720 --> 31:05.140
Your eyes are red.

31:05.220 --> 31:06.380
Your nose is red.

31:07.010 --> 31:08.270
Y-You're just pretty.

31:10.350 --> 31:11.130
Lie down now.

31:11.380 --> 31:13.380
Or your foot won't get enough blood.

31:18.980 --> 31:19.440
Come on.

31:26.510 --> 31:27.400
Are you feeling better?

31:27.400 --> 31:28.010
Yes.

31:29.000 --> 31:29.510
Sure.

31:32.010 --> 31:33.690
You were especially stunning

31:34.980 --> 31:35.840
on stage today.

31:43.480 --> 31:45.610
I got the smallest part in today's show,

31:45.610 --> 31:47.740
but you guys were still so supportive.

31:47.960 --> 31:49.160
That deeply moved me.

31:49.700 --> 31:50.770
In our eyes,

31:50.790 --> 31:52.120
you were singing a solo.

31:52.420 --> 31:53.550
We could see no one on stage,

31:53.550 --> 31:54.200
but you.

31:54.250 --> 31:56.250
We couldn't even hear anyone else sing.

31:56.250 --> 31:56.610
Okay.

31:57.880 --> 31:59.480
So your mouth isn't injured.

32:02.830 --> 32:03.610
I'm sure you will

32:03.610 --> 32:06.670
have tons of opportunities
to sing solos in the future.

32:07.420 --> 32:08.830
In my eyes...

32:15.110 --> 32:17.370
You're always in the center of the stage.

32:25.070 --> 32:26.070
Take a proper photo of me.

32:26.070 --> 32:26.580
Sure.

32:27.180 --> 32:27.600
Come on.

32:27.600 --> 32:28.260
Let's do it.

32:28.700 --> 32:29.320
Careful!

32:29.400 --> 32:29.930
I'm fine.

32:33.250 --> 32:34.410
Come on, look here.

32:34.920 --> 32:36.680
Now, look at the camera.

32:36.900 --> 32:39.470
One, two, three.

32:39.700 --> 32:40.160
Smile.

32:41.340 --> 32:42.370
One more photo.

32:42.460 --> 32:42.920
Come on.

32:44.070 --> 32:47.400
One, two, three. Smile!

32:48.420 --> 32:48.910
Done.

32:55.920 --> 32:56.650
This is nice.

32:57.160 --> 32:59.560
How can it be nice,
now that you're injured?

33:00.150 --> 33:02.350
I don't mind getting injured every day.

33:03.740 --> 33:05.000
What's that nonsense?

33:16.190 --> 33:16.990
So beautiful.

33:37.380 --> 33:38.440
Which meal is this?

33:38.570 --> 33:39.460
I just woke up.

33:41.940 --> 33:43.070
Did you drink again?

33:44.510 --> 33:45.110
Mr. Chu

33:45.140 --> 33:46.740
introduced me to a director.

33:49.640 --> 33:51.740
What role did you get this time?

33:52.000 --> 33:53.700
We didn't get into the details.

33:53.700 --> 33:54.980
All we had was dinner.

33:56.200 --> 33:56.960
Well...

33:57.810 --> 33:59.510
You always dine with them and get nothing.

33:59.510 --> 34:00.610
God knows what you guys

34:00.610 --> 34:01.940
talk about at the table.

34:02.770 --> 34:03.370
This is...

34:04.880 --> 34:05.720
Wait. Are you

34:05.830 --> 34:07.310
silly or what?

34:07.530 --> 34:09.940
Stop nagging me, okay?

34:10.610 --> 34:12.630
My head already hurts like hell.

34:16.730 --> 34:17.820
Are you sure this is proper food?

34:17.820 --> 34:19.080
E-Eat something else.

34:19.150 --> 34:20.440
What are you doing?

34:20.880 --> 34:22.570
I've been eating out these past few days.

34:22.570 --> 34:24.900
I just want to have
some home-made cooking.

34:24.900 --> 34:25.480
I'm not sure

34:25.480 --> 34:27.429
if what I'm making is any good.

34:29.000 --> 34:31.110
You want home-made cooking? No problem.

34:31.110 --> 34:32.719
Just come eat at my home.

34:33.610 --> 34:35.380
I don't mean anything particular by it.

34:35.380 --> 34:37.880
I would just love for you to try

34:37.900 --> 34:39.260
my parents' cooking.

34:39.320 --> 34:40.719
My dad is an amazing cook.

34:41.170 --> 34:43.690
He's good at cooking pork shoulder,
meatballs,

34:43.690 --> 34:45.010
and noodles in soybean paste

34:45.010 --> 34:47.730
with his secret recipes.

34:48.000 --> 34:49.130
You should try them.

34:52.800 --> 34:53.290
No,

34:53.360 --> 34:54.860
let me rephrase it.

34:54.900 --> 34:56.830
I just hope to introduce you

34:56.880 --> 34:58.600
to my parents

34:58.650 --> 35:00.230
over dinner,

35:00.280 --> 35:01.210
so you can

35:01.380 --> 35:02.960
get to know each other.

35:04.230 --> 35:04.960
Is that okay?

35:08.690 --> 35:10.220
Turn it off and come with me.

35:11.130 --> 35:11.860
Twist it that way.

35:11.860 --> 35:12.460
Which way?

35:12.530 --> 35:13.650
To the left.

35:14.000 --> 35:14.760
Lili,

35:15.760 --> 35:17.170
you may not trust me,

35:17.380 --> 35:19.240
but you do trust my father, right?

35:20.900 --> 35:21.860
My dad can arrange

35:21.860 --> 35:23.170
a comfortable job for you.

35:23.170 --> 35:25.070
All it takes is a word from him.

35:30.420 --> 35:31.480
Don't be like this.

35:31.840 --> 35:33.840
This is only our second time meeting.

35:33.840 --> 35:34.820
We were strangers

35:34.820 --> 35:36.260
the first time, but friends the next time!

35:36.260 --> 35:37.690
Please don't do this.

35:38.030 --> 35:39.090
What are you doing?

35:42.880 --> 35:44.410
The sun hasn't even set yet.

35:44.760 --> 35:45.610
What are you doing here,

35:45.610 --> 35:46.870
making all that noise?

35:47.070 --> 35:48.200
I heard everything.

35:48.380 --> 35:49.400
The girl is reluctant.

35:49.400 --> 35:50.840
You're being a rogue, you know?

35:50.840 --> 35:52.160
Who are you?

35:52.190 --> 35:53.450
None of your business.

35:53.980 --> 35:55.320
If you have a problem with me,

35:55.320 --> 35:57.360
let's go to
the joint security station nearby.

35:57.360 --> 35:58.000
We can spend a while there,

35:58.000 --> 35:58.400
buddy.

35:59.530 --> 36:00.860
He and I know each other.

36:01.070 --> 36:02.070
You know each other?

36:02.070 --> 36:02.920
We're dating!

36:04.630 --> 36:05.510
Dating?

36:06.150 --> 36:07.210
I don't care if you're dating

36:07.210 --> 36:07.940
or whatever.

36:08.570 --> 36:09.360
What you're doing here

36:09.360 --> 36:09.860
in broad daylight

36:09.860 --> 36:11.210
is just not appropriate.

36:11.210 --> 36:11.820
You know?

36:12.300 --> 36:13.780
If you're really dating,

36:13.980 --> 36:14.590
get intimate at home

36:14.590 --> 36:15.850
or somewhere private.

36:16.110 --> 36:17.550
Then you can do anything you want.

36:17.550 --> 36:19.000
But it's improper to behave like that here

36:19.000 --> 36:20.600
in front of people, isn't it?

36:20.820 --> 36:21.350
Alright.

36:21.480 --> 36:22.150
Today,

36:23.030 --> 36:24.090
I'll do a good deed.

36:25.190 --> 36:26.770
There's a hostel nearby.

36:27.030 --> 36:27.820
The cost is low,

36:27.820 --> 36:28.630
and the service is good.

36:28.630 --> 36:29.320
You can do whatever

36:29.320 --> 36:30.130
you want there.

36:30.130 --> 36:30.760
Isn't it nice?

36:30.760 --> 36:32.630
D-Did anyone ask to go to a hostel?

36:33.150 --> 36:34.780
I'm not going to a hostel!

36:34.900 --> 36:35.710
You creep.

36:36.340 --> 36:36.800
Lili!

36:37.320 --> 36:37.800
Lili!

36:38.110 --> 36:39.150
Let me take you to dinner!

36:39.150 --> 36:39.480
Look at that.

36:39.480 --> 36:40.880
Let's go have roast duck!

36:41.280 --> 36:42.950
How am I a creep now?

36:48.460 --> 36:49.000
Sir,

36:50.320 --> 36:51.320
our customers have all been

36:51.320 --> 36:53.360
driven away by that saxophone player.

36:53.360 --> 36:54.070
Is he still coming today?

36:54.070 --> 36:55.000
Of course he is.

36:55.570 --> 36:57.110
None of us will have any peace

36:57.110 --> 36:58.860
until he gets enough of that junk.

36:58.860 --> 36:59.550
He thinks he plays it

36:59.550 --> 37:00.170
so well.

37:00.170 --> 37:00.840
Dad,

37:01.460 --> 37:02.260
I'm back!

37:05.880 --> 37:07.140
Will you do me the honor

37:07.860 --> 37:08.820
of coming with me?

37:08.820 --> 37:10.680
What stunt are you pulling today?

37:11.400 --> 37:12.340
Don't think I won't beat you up

37:12.340 --> 37:13.940
just because you're a sweet talker.

37:13.940 --> 37:15.240
Beat me if necessary.

37:18.340 --> 37:19.200
Come here, Dad.

37:20.800 --> 37:21.800
Hello, Uncle Tao.

37:22.590 --> 37:23.390
-Hello.
-Dad,

37:23.650 --> 37:24.710
this is Shen Ranran.

37:24.710 --> 37:25.170
Ranran,

37:26.000 --> 37:27.000
this is my father.

37:30.460 --> 37:31.460
A friend of yours?

37:35.300 --> 37:35.960
Have a seat.

37:36.030 --> 37:37.250
After you, Uncle Tao.

37:37.510 --> 37:38.780
Do be seated.

37:40.130 --> 37:41.510
You bought so many things.

37:41.510 --> 37:43.000
She said she couldn't show up

37:43.000 --> 37:44.600
empty-handed for the visit.

37:51.030 --> 37:52.000
What do you mean by this?

37:52.000 --> 37:52.800
I'm telling you,

37:52.800 --> 37:53.940
if you mess with me today,

37:53.940 --> 37:54.900
you won't be able to leave this place,

37:54.900 --> 37:55.440
you know?

37:55.610 --> 37:56.360
It's not that, buddy.

37:56.360 --> 37:57.820
I just need a word with you.

37:58.110 --> 37:59.960
About what? Where's your girlfriend?

37:59.960 --> 38:00.840
She's gone to the bathroom.

38:00.840 --> 38:01.230
Well...

38:01.230 --> 38:01.590
I thought

38:01.590 --> 38:03.010
you two had gone for dinner.

38:03.010 --> 38:04.510
Are you familiar with the hostel

38:04.510 --> 38:05.570
you just mentioned?

38:05.570 --> 38:06.130
Yes.

38:06.190 --> 38:07.120
I own that place.

38:09.300 --> 38:11.030
So you were just hustling
for your hostel here?

38:11.030 --> 38:12.170
How was I hustling for my hostel?

38:12.170 --> 38:13.650
I did what I did for your own good.

38:13.650 --> 38:14.530
You would've been taken

38:14.530 --> 38:15.320
to the police station

38:15.320 --> 38:16.150
if that girl had screamed louder.

38:16.150 --> 38:17.230
Do you believe that?

38:17.230 --> 38:18.690
Thank you then. Thank you.

38:18.900 --> 38:19.420
Now tell me

38:19.420 --> 38:20.150
where the hotel is.

38:20.150 --> 38:21.610
I'll meet you there later.

38:22.780 --> 38:25.090
It's not far from here.
Just turn the corner ahead,

38:25.090 --> 38:26.220
and enter Luogu Hutong to look for

38:26.220 --> 38:27.300
the Seasons Change Hostel.

38:27.300 --> 38:28.940
Ask around. People all know it.

38:28.940 --> 38:30.400
Leave the door open for me!

38:30.820 --> 38:31.360
Listen,

38:31.400 --> 38:32.930
I get off work at 11:00 p.m.!

38:33.760 --> 38:35.630
-Just be seated.
-I'd like to help.

38:35.630 --> 38:37.510
Don't bother with that. Let him do it.

38:37.510 --> 38:38.050
Come on.

38:38.110 --> 38:39.710
Wash your hands and get ready to eat.

38:39.710 --> 38:40.900
Help yourself to whatever beverage

38:40.900 --> 38:42.030
you like over there.

38:42.320 --> 38:42.840
Auntie,

38:43.000 --> 38:44.460
why not let me help you
bring the dishes out?

38:44.460 --> 38:45.210
No need.

38:45.210 --> 38:46.900
Just sit back and wait here.

38:47.840 --> 38:48.770
Thanks, auntie.

38:49.230 --> 38:50.180
Honey!

38:50.940 --> 38:52.800
Slice the braised pork shoulder.

38:53.030 --> 38:54.120
Already done.

38:54.150 --> 38:55.750
I'm making the garlic sauce.

38:56.050 --> 38:56.730
That girl

38:56.730 --> 38:58.150
is quite pretty.

38:58.210 --> 38:59.880
Did our son say
what their relationship is?

38:59.880 --> 39:01.410
Just friends, aren't they?

39:01.780 --> 39:02.510
Liangliang!

39:03.230 --> 39:04.190
Get the dishes out.

39:04.190 --> 39:04.650
Coming.

39:07.860 --> 39:08.600
Which one?

39:10.070 --> 39:11.800
She's your girlfriend, right?

39:14.940 --> 39:16.140
Why are you like this?

39:16.170 --> 39:17.210
And why are you like this?

39:17.210 --> 39:18.670
You've brought many people home

39:18.670 --> 39:19.960
since childhood,

39:19.980 --> 39:21.760
but never a girl.

39:23.480 --> 39:24.540
Tell the truth now.

39:25.480 --> 39:26.540
Do the two of you...

39:27.100 --> 39:27.810
like her?

39:28.210 --> 39:29.490
Why ask us?

39:30.110 --> 39:31.130
If you like her,

39:31.190 --> 39:32.470
treat her well.

39:32.780 --> 39:34.230
Bring her home for dinner when you can.

39:34.230 --> 39:34.880
That's right.

39:34.880 --> 39:36.340
Anyway, I think she's very pretty.

39:36.340 --> 39:38.070
I also think she's very pretty.

39:38.650 --> 39:39.250
Oh, right.

39:40.480 --> 39:41.690
What's Ranran's zodiac sign?

39:41.690 --> 39:42.750
Pick a bowl for her.

39:43.550 --> 39:43.950
Right.

39:45.150 --> 39:45.800
Rat.

39:47.190 --> 39:48.470
Say it now.

39:48.610 --> 39:49.150
Rat!

39:50.150 --> 39:51.130
Go find the right bowl then.

39:51.130 --> 39:52.280
The three of us shouldn't be

39:52.280 --> 39:52.920
whispering here.

39:52.920 --> 39:53.670
She's been sitting there for a while.

39:53.670 --> 39:55.420
How is it appropriate?

39:56.360 --> 39:57.620
Get the dishes out now.

39:58.880 --> 40:00.140
Uncle Tao, Auntie Tao,

40:00.510 --> 40:01.920
today's dinner...

40:02.170 --> 40:03.400
is a real feast.

40:03.860 --> 40:05.230
Just some home-made dishes.

40:05.230 --> 40:05.820
We were worried

40:05.820 --> 40:07.420
that you wouldn't like the salty flavor

40:07.420 --> 40:08.250
in the north.

40:08.760 --> 40:09.280
Right?

40:10.170 --> 40:12.380
I really love these noodles
in soybean paste.

40:12.380 --> 40:13.960
Liangliang kept telling me

40:14.070 --> 40:14.690
that his cooking

40:14.690 --> 40:16.170
was not as good as yours,

40:16.210 --> 40:17.690
and insisted that I come over for dinner.

40:17.690 --> 40:18.030
Yes.

40:18.280 --> 40:20.460
I learned it from my mom and dad.

40:21.300 --> 40:22.070
I mean,

40:22.190 --> 40:24.790
you two make it
in a more authentic way than I do.

40:26.260 --> 40:27.610
-Hurry, try the food.
-Come on.

40:27.610 --> 40:28.710
Come on, dig in.

40:29.070 --> 40:29.380
Mom,

40:29.420 --> 40:30.530
-focus on your portion.
-I can do it...

40:30.530 --> 40:31.790
And I'll focus on mine.

40:32.920 --> 40:33.360
Fine.

40:34.150 --> 40:35.350
You have some of this.

40:35.440 --> 40:35.940
Here.

40:38.820 --> 40:39.650
Ranran,

40:40.050 --> 40:41.180
how are you adapting

40:41.210 --> 40:42.900
to the life in a small hostel in the north

40:42.900 --> 40:44.190
as a girl from the south?

40:44.190 --> 40:45.210
I'm adapting well.

40:45.210 --> 40:46.630
Although the place is small,

40:46.630 --> 40:48.360
we are very happy living there.

40:48.440 --> 40:48.990
Well,

40:49.320 --> 40:51.260
mainly because I'm around, right?

40:53.800 --> 40:56.110
Right. Liangliang takes great care of me.

40:56.110 --> 40:57.050
That's the right thing to do.

40:57.050 --> 40:58.320
You young people should take care

40:58.320 --> 41:00.070
of each other
since you're always together.

41:00.070 --> 41:03.270
That's the only way to put my mind
and my husband's at ease.

41:03.420 --> 41:04.900
You have high cholesterol and blood sugar.

41:04.900 --> 41:06.050
How can you eat this?

41:06.840 --> 41:08.500
Ranran, have some more.

41:09.230 --> 41:09.610
Thank you, auntie.

41:09.610 --> 41:10.510
You look very thin.

41:10.510 --> 41:11.640
You should eat more.

41:11.960 --> 41:12.530
Try this.

41:15.110 --> 41:15.480
Dad,

41:16.230 --> 41:17.690
Mom is actually asking you

41:18.000 --> 41:19.460
to have more lean meat.

41:21.070 --> 41:22.130
That piece is fine.

41:22.630 --> 41:23.670
-Delicious!
-How is it?

41:23.670 --> 41:25.200
I'll stop my diet for today.

41:25.860 --> 41:26.960
That's the spirit.

41:27.800 --> 41:28.600
Well, this...

41:29.210 --> 41:31.140
My dad has a secret recipe for this.

41:31.190 --> 41:31.900
A family recipe

41:31.900 --> 41:33.230
that he'll pass it to me.

41:34.480 --> 41:36.080
I made it too salty this time.

41:36.860 --> 41:38.320
I'll pass the recipe to Liangliang,

41:38.320 --> 41:39.650
so he can make it for you.

41:41.950 --> 41:43.380
How do you know it's too salty?

41:43.380 --> 41:44.690
You sneaked a bite behind me, didn't you?

41:44.690 --> 41:46.420
I tasted it to see
if it was properly seasoned.

41:46.420 --> 41:48.230
Hey, there's much oil in it.

41:48.630 --> 41:50.170
You just wouldn't listen to me,

41:50.170 --> 41:50.770
would you?

41:52.690 --> 41:53.340
Ranran,

41:54.260 --> 41:56.030
is filming tiring for you?

41:56.420 --> 41:57.000
I heard

41:57.030 --> 41:58.070
actresses can't even have

41:58.070 --> 41:59.270
hot meals. Is it true?

41:59.670 --> 42:01.030
Mom, let's eat first,

42:01.170 --> 42:03.570
before the food gets old.
We can talk later.

42:05.000 --> 42:06.590
W-What's going on?

42:08.530 --> 42:09.330
Oh, Ranran...

42:11.780 --> 42:12.710
Anything wrong?

42:13.530 --> 42:15.730
No, I'm just getting a little homesick.

42:17.050 --> 42:18.110
I spoke out of turn.

42:18.640 --> 42:19.520
Don't be upset.

42:19.550 --> 42:20.570
If you ever feel homesick,

42:20.570 --> 42:21.530
just come over here.

42:21.530 --> 42:23.570
My husband
will cook something delicious for you.

42:23.570 --> 42:24.730
Bring your clothes over too.

42:24.730 --> 42:25.990
I'll wash them for you.

42:27.420 --> 42:28.950
A girl living away from home

42:28.960 --> 42:30.550
should take good care of herself

42:30.550 --> 42:31.950
and not worry her family.

42:32.340 --> 42:32.920
Right?

42:33.390 --> 42:35.210
Let Ranran eat.

42:35.360 --> 42:36.810
Don't nag her ear off.

42:37.920 --> 42:39.260
I'm just overjoyed.

42:40.260 --> 42:41.070
Eat up.

42:41.210 --> 42:42.510
We'll have plenty of time to talk, right?

42:42.510 --> 42:44.130
Come on, clink our glasses too.

42:44.130 --> 42:45.130
Right, together.

42:46.110 --> 42:46.910
How very nice.

42:50.010 --> 42:50.560
Ranran,

42:50.690 --> 42:52.150
try the soy-braised beef.

42:54.570 --> 42:55.500
Now even I can reach it.
